In [23]:
def getMesh(x, fx, fy):
    mfz = [ [0]*len(x) for i in range(len(x))]
    for i in range(len(x)):
        for j in range(len(x)): 
            if not((fx[i] == 0.) ^ (fy[j] == 0)):
                mfz[i][j] = (fx[i] + fy[j]) / 2  #  not((fx[i] == 0.) ^ (fy[j] == 0))
    return mfz

mfz1 = np.array(getMesh(x, mfx1, mfy1))
mfz2 = np.array(getMesh(x, mfx2, mfy2))

mfz1 = mfz1
mfz2 = mfz2 * -1

abbas = mfz1 + mfz2
